citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:51am on
29-Aug-19.
The inspector was able to make contact with the Licensee's Son. He was able to confirm that no one was available
for inspection at that time.
